Injustice:  
 
The male thought hard on this, it was not something he readily understood.  He supposed Windlord cared about her, but he did not really understand how exactly he felt.  Describing an emotion was difficult, he could not understand.
 
"I'm not sure.  I do not understand the emotions Windlord feels.  I just don't."
